---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../components/Text.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import abdeljalil_1 from "../assets/images/abdeljalil_1.webp";
import abdeljalil_2 from "../assets/images/abdeljalil_2.webp";
import abdeljalil_3 from "../assets/images/abdeljalil_3.webp";
---

<MainLayout title="Explore our farm">
  <main class="grid grid-cols-6 px-5 lg:px-10 lg:grid-cols-12">

<!-- first section start -->

<!-- headings start -->
<div class="col-start-1 col-span-6 lg:col-span-9 gap-2.5"> 
<Heading htmlheading="h1" size="small" font="display">Explore our farm</Heading>
<Heading htmlheading="h2" size="medium" font="heading">Meet Abdeljalil</Heading>
</div>
<!-- headings slut -->

<!-- text-picture-text start -->
<div class="py-5 lg:py-10 col-start-1 col-span-6 lg:col-start-4 lg:col-span-4"> 
<Text stylingclasses="mb-5 lg:mb-10">The story of our olive oil begins with a man: Abdeljalil. Raised with six siblings in the vibrant old town of Marrakesh, he grew up with an insatiable curiosity for the world. That passion led him to become a life science teacher, dedicated to showing how nature evolves and works together. He passed this same spirit to his sons, Marouane and Anas, teaching them to see the world, its people, and its wonders with open minds.</Text>
<Image src={abdeljalil_2} alt="Picture of Abdeljalil that stands between two olive trees" />
<Text stylingclasses="mt-5 lg:mt-10">Abdeljalil spent much of his free time on the family farm, teaching his children to care for their century old Haouzia olive trees. These trees, unique to Marrakesh's Haouz province, thrive only in this land's particular climate, producing olives with an intense, unmistakable flavor.</Text>
</div>
<!-- text-picture-text slut -->

<!-- picture left-sided start-->
<div class="mb-5 lg:-mt-30 col-start-3 col-span-4 lg:col-start-10 lg:col-span-3"> 
<Image src={abdeljalil_3} alt="Picture of Abdeljalil and his sons" />
</div>
<!-- picture left-sided slut-->

<!-- last picture start -->
<div class="mb-10 lg:-mt-132 col-start-1 col-span-6 lg:col-start-9 lg:col-span-4"> 
<Image src={abdeljalil_1} alt="Picture of Abdeljalil by an olive oil machine" />
</div>
<!-- last picture slut-->

<!-- first section slut -->
  
  
  
  
  
  
  </main>
</MainLayout>
